				<h4>About the Information We Collect</h4>

				<p>You can visit this website without letting us know who you are or disclosing any personal data. Our site will (as numerous sites do) place a "cookie" (a data file) on your computer's hard drive which permits the server to recognize when it visits again to track navigational data on our website. This cookie is not used to acquire any personal information. The data is utilized for internal purposes, for example, to enhance site navigation and to collect statistics on our promotions. It is not shared with anyone other than NexXStars subsidiaries. If you do not wish to allow cookies, you can set your browser to block them. Moreover, there are cases on this site where we may need to gather personal data from you for a specific reason, for example, to provide you information that you request. The data gathered from you may include your name, location, phone or email address.</p>

				<p>We utilize a third-party technology to place our ads on other sites. This will place a cookie on your computer when you see our advertisement. These cookies won't hold any data that identifies you, (for example, your name or email address) yet they will hold a random number that specific to your browser and might be recognized by a beacon on our site when you navigate to our webpage from one of our ads. This permits us to stay informed regarding the number of visitors we have to our site and from what ads they entered, with the goal that we can measure the adequacy of our ads and promotion positions. The privacy policy of the sites on which we advertise, and through which the cookies are introduced should inform you of the same, and you may certainly set your browser to block cookies. To find out more about the third-party advertisement technology that we utilize, cookies, and opting out, please email us at info@nexxstars.com.</p>

				<h4>Data Security</h4>

				<p>We uphold strict regulations to ensure your data from unauthorized access. We restrict access to your data to NexXStars employees responding to your request or solicitation. Employees who abuse personal data are liable to disciplinary action.</p>

				<h4>How We Use Information We Collect</h4>

				<p>By submitting a form on any of the NexXStars web properties or online offers, you authorize NexXStars and affiliates to contact you by phone or email regarding this offer and any new offers made accessible later on. Data that is gathered is not used to personally recognize you and rather is collected to measure the amount of visits, time spent on the site, pages seen, and so on. We utilize this data to measure the utilization of our site and to enhance the substance of our site.</p>

				<p>The point when other data is gathered from you, for example, your name and email address, we by and large let you know at the time of collection how we will utilize the data. More often than not, we utilize the particular data you give just to respond to your request or to process your solicitation, (for example, to inquire about our services). This data may be imparted to other NexXStars organizations if relevant to satisfy your request or for related purposes.</p>

				<p>We may share the personal data you give with outside organizations or partners. These organizations are contractually bound to utilize personal data we share with them solely to perform the services we have contracted them for. We don't share, sell, or lease personal data about you to any outside organizations for their marketing use. We will disclose your data upon your request, in the event that we are bound by law to do so, or in other legally restricted circumstances (for instance, to secure your record from fraud).</p>

				<p>Assuming that you enroll with one of NexXStars's entities on the web, they may utilize this data to give you custom data about NexXStars's products or services as they related to your business needs. They might additionally place a cookie to be able to provide you with custom data.</p>

				<p>This site is not for persons under 13 years of age. We don't intentionally request or gather data from or about kids, and we don't purposely advertise our products or services to children.</p>

				<h4>Links to third-party sites</h4>

				<p>Our site may link to different destinations. While we seek to link just to sites that share our security standards, we are not responsible for the practices utilized by different sites.</p>
				
				
